#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:6
msgid "This course enables participants to plan and implement biodiversity data mobilization efforts effectively using accepted community standards. Its aim is to increase the volume, richness and quality of the data published through the GBIF network."
msgstr ""

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/data-mobilization/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:8
