msgid "Upon completion of the course and successful submission and assessment of assignments (by trainers), participants have the opportunity to earn a digital certification https://openbadgefactory.com/en/about-open-badges/[Open Badges]. See xref:assessments-certification.adoc[Assessment and certification] for more details."
msgstr ""

